The paper discusses a generic online parallel learning framework for large margin models, which is a topic related to machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) since the paper focuses on parallel technology. Other possible categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) since the paper discusses popular large margin algorithms and their performance in experiments.
